data.description: SELLER WILL CREDIT $5000 TOWARDS BUYERS INTEREST RATE BUY DOWN WITH ACCEPTABLE OFFER - Low Fayette County taxes! Beautiful 5BR/3BA home nestled on 1 acre in Lakes of Lou Monta. Formal Dining Room; Great Room; Kitchen w/double ovens, breakfast bar, storage & pantry; Hearth Room w/FP; primary bed down w/updated luxury bath; 2nd bed down w/private bath; 3 beds & bath up. Outside features 3 car garage, garden area, storage shed, fenced yard, quiet cove - Enjoy the swing & view of the pond!
